name: International Webinar on 3D Printing and Additive Manufacturing
content: 3D Printing Webinar 2020 welcomes everyone around the globe to attend the “ International Webinar on 3D Printing and Additive Manufacturing” which will be held during May 15, 2020 at Paris, France . This is going to be the largest and most promising international Webinar where 3D Printing, professionals, and decision-makers will come to discuss various aspects. 3D Printing Webinar directs towards main issues as well as future strategies of the 3D Printing, research, technology, and innovation.This gathering gives an incredible chance to discuss about the most recent advancements inside the field. The conference runs with the theme “From Your Imagination to a 3D Model”. For more information about this conference visit below link: https://www.meetingsint.com/webinars/3dprinting
